      {
        "question": "Can it build a DCF model?",
        "answer": "Yes. It provides a DCF workflow with free cash flow, WACC, terminal value, intrinsic value, and sensitivity analysis."
      },
      {
        "question": "Can it screen stocks?",
        "answer": "Yes. It includes value and small-cap growth screening workflows with adjustable thresholds and ranked outputs."
      },
      {
        "question": "Does it provide investment advice?",
        "answer": "No. Outputs are research summaries and frameworks for reference, not personalized investment recommendations."
      },
      {
